Check fitted model

Source: R/check_model.R
check_model.Rd

Check fitted model

check_model(fit = NULL)

Arguments

fit

A fitted model, as obtained from fit_model().

Value

Model checks on console and graphical window.

Examples

data(web)
dt <- prepare_data(mat = web, sampl.eff = rep(20, nrow(web)))
fit <- fit_model(dt)
